25|$|The Union for a Popular Movement (UMP), Sarkozy's party, won a {{majority}} at the June 2007 legislative election, although {{by less than}} expected. In July, the UMP majority, seconded by the Nouveau Centre, ratified one of Sarkozy's electoral promises, which was to partially revoke the <b>inheritance</b> <b>tax.</b> The <b>inheritance</b> <b>tax</b> formerly brought eight billion euros into state coffers.|$|E
